'''Dr. Mohamed Zahir Hussain''' ([[Dhivehi]]:ޑރ. މުޙައްމަދު ޒާހިރު ޙުސައިން) was the former Minister of sports of the [[Maldives]].
==Genealogy==
Dr. Mohamed Zahir Hussain is the son of Hussain Didi son of Maryam Didi daughter of Abdulla Didi son of Hussain Didi son of Mohamed Didi son of princess Maryam Kan'baa daughter of Sultan Ibrahim Iskandhar II son of Sultan Muzaffar Mohamed Imaduddin II of [[Dhiyamigili dynasty]].
==External links==
* [http://www.maldivianroots.com Maldivian Roots.com - Online Maldivian Genealogist]

